summary: An ordinance appropriating money from the Water Fund to H. L. Hulman, in payment of claim for personal injuries to wife, Addie Hulman, File No. 147742, and directing the City Comptroller to cancel warrant in the sum of Twenty-five dollars ($25.00) on the Water Fund, drawn in favor of H. L. Hulman, under authority of Ordinance No. 65593, and repealing said Ordinance No. 65593.
